verse.lines:
{lang-eng}There is a name I love to hear,
I love to speak its worth;
It sounds like music in mine ear,
The sweetest name on earth.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}It tells me of a Savior’s love,
Who died to set me free;
It tells me of His precious blood,
The sinner’s perfect plea.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}It tells of One whose loving heart
Can feel my deepest woe;
Who in my sorrow bears a part,
That none can bear below.{/lang-eng}
